===Etymology 1===
Old English [[blac|blāc]].

====Adjective====
'''bleak'''

# Without [[color]]; [[pale]]; [[pallid]].
# [[desolate|Desolate]] and [[exposed]]; [[swept]] by cold [[winds]].
# Cold and [[cutting]]; [[cheerless]]; as, a bleak blast.

